        <item>
            <title>v1.0.0-beta</title>
            <pubDate>Sun, 17 Feb 2025 09:05:58 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>1.0.0</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>v1.0.0-beta</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>13.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h3>Changes in Overview v1.0.0-beta</h3>
                <h4>Features:</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Keyboard shortcut system replacing hotkeys, allowing multiple window titles per shortcut</li>
                    <li>Automatic update feature added, with beta channel option and menu bar item</li>
                    <li>Implemented developer ID Apple notarization for direct distribution</li>
                    <li>Permission manager now handles permission state and setup window</li>
                    <li>Context menu item added to stop capture/return to selection view</li>
                    <li>Option added to show both application name and window title in overlay</li>
                    <li>Dock icon now shows while in permission setup or while settings window is open</li>
                </ul>
                <h4>Bug Fixes:</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Multiple hotkey bugs resolved in switch to keyboard shortcuts</li>
                </ul>
            ]]>
